message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for $170. I believe it will be very valuable for you.
I'm interested in the product, but I was thinking more along the lines of $90. Can you meet me at that price?
Bob, thanks for the offer, but $90 is too low for me. Could you do $140?
I'm still interested in the product, but I was thinking more along the lines of $110. Can you meet me at that price?
